<li><a href="#1%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E4%BC%98%E7%82%B9">1.官方镜像优点</a></li>
<li><a href="#2%E7%83%A7%E5%86%99%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0ssh%E7%A9%BA%E7%99%BD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0boot%E7%9B%98%E9%A2%84%E5%9F%8Bwifi">2.烧写镜像，添加SSH空白文件到boot盘，预埋wifi</a></li>
